{"tid":2385040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解連登仔成日將美國當係全球民主國家的指標？","createTime":"2021-01-28T23:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T03:47:47.000Z","uid":100680,"like":22,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"04d851c6e89d068774d8b054fa33e9ac20bd7817","tid":2385040,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:00:06.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post有感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2384784/page/4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2384784/page/4</a><br />\n裏面成大堆連登仔話美國作為全球最民主國家的指標點點點點點.........<br />\n<br />\n其實連登仔知唔知美國不嬲都唔係全球最民主的國家黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國內裏仲行緊共和制<br />\n每年全球民主指數排名美國都好落後下<br />\n排名機構仲將美國的民主制度稱為&quot;不完全的民主&quot;<br />\n真正做到完全民主化係果堆北歐國家<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hant%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2595%25B0&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1wwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=b1af9851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hant/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n唔明點解連登仔成日將美國當係民主指標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8829ad9c8bcc13a62ddbd587838cfe3d6e1b674","tid":2385040,"uid":124021,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:25:58.000Z","msg":"佢哋睇得多支那新聞<br />\n成日美國乜美國物<br />\n<br />\n一向都知美國一向都冇乜民主"},{"pid":"7d8ac9a6b476c1089208be3bc6bd99a1dd97ba5a","tid":2385040,"uid":129676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:27:23.000Z","msg":"民主只係一種理想<br />\n只係支持呢個理想既人口分佈率"},{"pid":"1331317b158806981c8f5e054a9ec544b512c4b1","tid":2385040,"uid":121697,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T23:28:46.000Z","msg":"大選完左就無人當過係指標啦"},{"pid":"5e83efb8c846439928d0a8677c59ec7ceff9d761","tid":2385040,"uid":231080,"like":7,"dislike":21,"score":-14,"cited